high_descs: Go straight, then turn right, then go left to go around the coffee table, then turn to face the rightmost couch cushion.
Pick up the pillow on the rightmost couch cushion.
Turn right, then turn right to go around the table, the go straight, toward the lamp in the corner ahead.
anns.task_desc: Examine a cushion by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the sofa.
Pick up the white cushion on the sofa.
Turn around and walk to the tall lamp by the picture on the wall.
anns.task_desc: Look at the cushion under the light of the tall lamp.

high_descs: Walk forward and go to the couch.
Pick up the pillow on the couch.
Turn around and go to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a pillow under the lamp.

high_descs: Cross the room towards the white couch, hang a right and turn to your left to face a small white pillow.
Pick up the small white pillow on the white couch.
Turn to your right, head towards the television, hang a right until you reach a tall lamp in the corner against the wall.
anns.task_desc: Examine a pillow near the light of a tall lamp.
